{"id": "1207639640140414996", "channel_id": "1207639640140414996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176579168448823471", "author_name": "llhwwc_89248", "author_bot": false, "content": "融灾5：非常难，道中压力巨大（但有造物缓冲），BOSS是阴间24\n\n阵容栗艾朵奥，核心是钥令的注射守护。\n\n本关要点有三个：\n\n1.分配好资源死抗抗24大招，奥义抗纷乱切割。\n2.不要急于投毒，前期唯一任务是防守攒救救我，以及叠奥吉尔力量，大概56个回合后再开始投毒。\n3.前期卖死抗，后期狂气转不动+绿炎卡手卡炸的时候救救我连拍手打死灭。\n\n融灾4：难度较小，BOSS是笨比尤乌，毫无输出，模仿上期融灾5，诺缔拉超维空间里无脑叠反击，后期卡好尤乌大招间隔潘狄娅输出即可。\n\n注意造物效果能够触发2次觉醒卡，2次灵感这些，但不能触发2次伤痛之鳍（命轮）\n\n融灾3：难度较小，造物强度逆天，希洛闭眼乱杀，我希洛莉莉这队几乎毫无练度的情况下碾过去了。\n\n1/2白给关就不多说了。\n\n目前融灾5还有其它小伙伴用希洛莉莉，红花阿神，炖鸡过关，思路很多可多多尝试。", "timestamp": "2024-02-15T10:48:47.069000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1207639640962637835", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-15-18-39-24-304_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 138687, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1207639640140414996/1207639640962637835/Screenshot_2024-02-15-18-39-24-304_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb1c8f&is=69f9cb0f&hm=0629d430419e107638bd09726d0c22d1446c962061bf246cec887b6f6f64f918&"}, {"id": "1207639641436463144", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-15-18-39-25-898_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 139202, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1207639640140414996/1207639641436463144/Screenshot_2024-02-15-18-39-25-898_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb1c8f&is=69f9cb0f&hm=0cdd755d9a96dc96f697368a169d208466e8f46a0612364c0125c660304f3db0&"}, {"id": "1207639641964941312", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-15-18-39-27-474_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 141746, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1207639640140414996/1207639641964941312/Screenshot_2024-02-15-18-39-27-474_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb1c8f&is=69f9cb0f&hm=3a4435f5cccef13b7bebcae57a155cb74811d909e673c12d51cd10ab7502b0ce&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, 